Regulation (EC) No 1619/1999 is amended as follows:
1. the entries corresponding to cod in zone VIIb-k, VIII, IX, CECAF 37.1.1 (Community waters) and sprat in zone Skagerrak and Kattegat shall be removed from the Annex;
2. the entries of Annex I to this Regulation shall replace the corresponding entries in the Annex;
3. the entries of Annex II to this Regulation shall be inserted in the Annex.
